From Grayson Walker Subject Re Changing oil by Why crawl under the car at all I have a machine I got for my boat that pulls the oil out under suction through the dip stick It does an excellent job and by moving the suction tube around you can get more old oil out than by using the drain I think I paid at E B The oil goes into a steel gal can wait until it cools and decant into your favorite I use soft drink Easy to take them down to the local oil recycle FORZA